&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; It&#39;d be really nice for those of us that want to script heritrix to
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; load up an order (especially based on a recovery), then be able to
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; modify it using JMX before launching the crawl.
